      <body>
         <p>Using what you found in the question above, summarize the probability distribution of X in a table.</p>
      </body>
      <short_answer id="A"/>
      <part>
         <response input="A" match="*" score="1"/>
         <explanation>
            <image src="../../webcontent/flash/_u4_m3_lbdtutor1d_image1.jpg"/>
            <p>Note that P(X = 3) = 1/4 since by the addition principle (for disjoint events):</p>
            <p>P(X = 3) = P(GGB) + P(GGG) = 1/8 + 1/8 = 1/4</p>
         </explanation>
